OL,4,CEscobar pub accused of glorifying drug
OL,5,Clord's reign of terror
OL,6, Owners of a South American-themed bar
OL,7, that shares its name with notorious
OL,8, Colombian drug lord Pablo Escobar have
OL,9, been urged to rethink their branding.
OL,11,FColombians living in Nottingham said
OL,12,Fcalling the venue Escobar was in poor
OL,13,Ftaste, given the pain and death
OL,14,Finflicted by the famous cartel boss.
OL,16,FThey also criticised a mural inside the
OL,17,Fbar that appears to depict Escobar.
OL,19,FA bar spokesperson said the venue's
OL,20,Fname was just a "play on words" and the
OL,21,Fmural was not based on Pablo Escobar.
